<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Unity Flower Store</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #ffd1c4;
        }
        .hero {
            background-image: url('https://example.com/flower-background.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero-text {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .intro h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .intro p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .feature h3 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feature p {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 1em;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .user-buttons {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .user-buttons p {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .user-buttons button {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 5px;
            font-size: 1em;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .user-buttons button:hover {
            background-color: #e65c55;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('./partials/nav') %>
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Welcome to Unity Flowers</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="user-buttons">
          <p>Change User ID:</p>
          <form action="/changeUserID" method="POST">
            <button>User ID 0</button>
            <input type="hidden" name="userID" value="0">
          </form>
          <form action="/changeUserID" method="POST">
            <button>User ID 1</button>
            <input type="hidden" name="userID" value="1">
          </form>
          <form action="/changeUserID" method="POST">
            <button>User ID 2</button>
            <input type="hidden" name="userID" value="2">
          </form>
          <form action="/changeUserID" method="POST">
            <button>User ID 3</button>
            <input type="hidden" name="userID" value="3">
          </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="intro">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Unity Flowers, we are committed to providing the freshest and most vibrant flowers for every occasion. From romantic roses to cheerful tulips, our selection is sure to brighten anyone's day.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Wide Variety</h3>
                <p>Explore a wide range of flowers, from classic roses to exotic orchids.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Freshness Guaranteed</h3>
                <p>We ensure that every flower you purchase is as fresh and beautiful as possible.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Fast Delivery</h3>
                <p>Enjoy fast and reliable delivery, so your flowers arrive in perfect condition.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Customer Support</h3>
                <p>Our friendly customer support team is here to help with any questions or concerns.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>2024 Unity Flowers Store</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
